{"title":"Maxxis Shorty Gen 2 MTB mid-spike mud tire gains traction, reduces size & weight","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/22/maxxis-shorty-gen-2-mtb-mid-spike-mud-tire-gains-traction-reduces-size-weight/","date":1613998836000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>When things get sloppy, mid-spike tires are a way to increase traction without going mud tire. Maxxis recommends their Shorty mid-spike for wet or extreme dust conditions – but most riders will probably reach for their Shorties when mud is in the forecast. Now, the Shorty you know and love has been improved for even better grip and reduced weight thanks to the new sizing…</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Maxxis-Shorty-mid-spike-mud-tire-update-2021-mountain-bike-MTB-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Maxxis-Shorty-mid-spike-mud-tire-update-2021-mountain-bike-MTB-1-e1613974158439.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x408/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"Maxxis Shorty Gen 2 MTB mid-spike mud tire tread\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1012\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Maxxis-Shorty-mid-spike-mud-tire-update-2021-mountain-bike-MTB-1-e1613974158439.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x408/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Maxxis-Shorty-mid-spike-mud-tire-update-2021-mountain-bike-MTB-1-e1613974158439.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Maxxis-Shorty-mid-spike-mud-tire-update-2021-mountain-bike-MTB-1-e1613974158439-297x250.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploa